column2: SELECT   o.GALname,   o.ra,   o.dec,   o.z,   p.objId,   p.cmodelFlux_u,   p.cmodelFlux_g,   p.cmodelFlux_r,   p.cmodelFlux_i,   p.cmodelFlux_z,   p.cmodelFluxIvar_u,   p.cmodelFluxIvar_g,   p.cmodelFluxIvar_r,     p.cmodelFluxIvar_i,     p.cmodelFluxIvar_z INTO mydb.pisco_sdss_cmodelflux FROM mydb.pisco_final_galaxies AS o   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(o.ra, o.dec, #) AS near   INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary AS pp ON pp.objID=near.objID   INNER JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objID=pp.objID   INNER JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON pp.objID=p.objID
